snippet.title: Top 7 Horrifying and Mysterious Creatures

localized.description:
A video I created about some creatures that allegedly have been spotted around the world. Watch the video to learn more :-)

It includes: Pope Lick Monster, Goatman, Canvey Island Monster, Sigbin, Bunyip, Lizard Man of Scape Ore Swamp, Owlman, Flatwoods Monster, Jersey Devil, Dover Demon.

Music:
Night of Chaos - Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
